Instructions for building radmon_angle executable.
	
   1) Load the build module appropriate for your Machine:
     i.)
        WCOSS:
           "module use -a ../../modulefiles/wcoss"     
        CRAY:
           "module use -a ../../modulefiles"     
        THEIA:
           "module use -a ../../modulefiles/theia"
     ii.)
        WCOSS & THEIA:
           "module load RadMonBuild"
        CRAY:
           "module load RadMonBuild.cray"

   2)  Optional:  verify all prerequisites are met by typing:
	"make check_prereqs"

   3) Build the executable by typing:
        "make"
   
   4) Move the executable to the ../../exec directory by typing:
   	"make install"
  
   5) Unload the build module:
        "module unload RadMonBuild"

